        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="mt-20 p-8 bg-[#0e3146] border-t-4 border-[#e9691e] rounded-b-xl">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
          <div>
            <p class="font-['Fira+Code'] text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Jurisdicción_Principal</p>
            <p class="text-white font-['Orbitron'] text-sm tracking-tighter">SUCRE, BOLIVIA / LATAM OPERACIONES</p>
          </div>
